Correction Statement for Fig. S3

Thanks to a reader’s reminder, we noticed a mistake in our Fig. S3, where the scatter points in the original Fig. S3a,b were incorrectly identical in distribution and number that compares crop yields with mean growing-season temperatures for wheat in the USA and India. After checking the data, we noticed that we had made a mistake when plotting the data by selecting a wrong line in our code. For those who are using our data, please pay attention to this mistake. The corrected Fig. S3ab are shown in the document “fig S3 - correction.pdf”.
We are sincerely grateful for the reader for pointing us to this mistake.

Rong Wang
1st July 2026
